{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2018}} {{Use British English|date=February 2018}} '''Dudley Knowles''' ({{IPAc-en|n|oʊ|l|z}}; 1947, [[Lancashire]] – 26 October 2014) was a [[United Kingdom|British]] [[political philosopher]] and professor at [[Glasgow University]]. He was widely known for his influential book ''Political Philosophy'' (2001).
